dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: nahiyat Khan Bani Sa'd wa Mahrut wa shu'bat Ba'qubah
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misaha al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Khan Bani Sa'd and Mahrut districts, Ba'quba region.] Alternate title: Liwa' Diyala: Qada' Daltawah wa Baqubah: nahiyat Khan Bani Sa'd wa Mahrut wa shu'bat Ba'qubah. [Diyala province: Daltawah and Ba'qubah districts: Khan Bani Sa'd and Mahrut sections, Ba'qubah region.] Relief shown by hachures, form lines, and contour lines at .5 meter intervals. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1926. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
